Bagaimana jika kami tidak mau?

474
00:33:10,238 --> 00:33:13,492
Kalau begitu, akan jadi masalah besar
bagi kita semua.

475
00:33:13,575 --> 00:33:16,369
DETEKTIF HAEGYONG LEE,
POLISI REMAJA WANITA SEOUL JUNG-GU

476
00:33:21,625 --> 00:33:23,835
Apa itu akan sepadan dengan masalah ini?

477
00:33:31,384 --> 00:33:32,594
Seharusnya tak kucoba ini.

478
00:33:33,428 --> 00:33:34,387
Matikan rokok kalian.

479
00:33:34,721 --> 00:33:36,681
Ambil puntungnya. Ayo buang.

480
00:33:37,224 --> 00:33:39,559
Kalian sangat hebat.

481
00:33:40,393 --> 00:33:42,145
Jadi? Sudah selesai?

482
00:33:43,355 --> 00:33:45,106
Dasar berengsek...

483
00:33:45,524 --> 00:33:46,358
Minhee.

484
00:33:47,359 --> 00:33:48,193
Minhee Seo.

485
00:33:53,532 --> 00:33:54,658
Anak-anak muda itu.

486
00:33:57,035 --> 00:33:59,996
Ambil semua puntung rokok!
Buang semua!

487
00:34:31,945 --> 00:34:33,113
Hei, ada apa?

488
00:34:33,989 --> 00:34:36,199
Pilih antara daging sapi atau babi.

489
00:34:36,283 --> 00:34:38,076
Bukan. Dengar.

490
00:34:38,994 --> 00:34:39,828
Dia?

491
00:34:39,911 --> 00:34:42,205
Yang lebih sedikit akan melakukannya.

492
00:34:42,289 --> 00:34:43,915
- Kau berikan?
- Satu, dua, tiga.

493
00:34:43,999 --> 00:34:45,792
Hal yang kita lakukan keesokan harinya.

494
00:34:46,710 --> 00:34:47,836
Kau tak ingat?

495
00:34:56,678 --> 00:34:58,221
KANG BBANG: MISI SELESAI

496
00:35:01,308 --> 00:35:03,893
Mari putuskan hubungan kita.

497
00:35:04,894 --> 00:35:05,770
Apa maksudmu?

498
00:35:06,396 --> 00:35:07,856
Maafkan aku, Berengsek.

499
00:35:08,565 --> 00:35:09,899
Karena memukulmu saat itu.

500
00:35:11,359 --> 00:35:14,571
Penampilan 100 hariku juga gagal karenamu.

501
00:35:15,614 --> 00:35:16,614
Sekarang kita impas.

502
00:35:16,698 --> 00:35:18,700
Lalu kenapa kau...

503
00:35:19,492 --> 00:35:20,910
- melakukannya?
- Apa?

504
00:35:22,037 --> 00:35:22,871
Pewarna.

505
00:35:23,371 --> 00:35:25,206
Loker dan kursiku.

506
00:35:25,290 --> 00:35:26,124
Apa?

507
00:35:27,125 --> 00:35:29,586
Kursi apa? Apa maksud si berengsek ini?

508
00:35:31,963 --> 00:35:33,923
Intinya, kita sudah berbaikan.

509
00:35:38,636 --> 00:35:40,680
Beri tahu Baeggyul, ya?

510
00:35:53,860 --> 00:35:57,322
Oji.

511
00:36:00,367 --> 00:36:01,660
Berikutnya kelasku?

512
00:36:03,411 --> 00:36:06,664
Hei, aku dengar rumor kontroversial.

513
00:36:07,165 --> 00:36:07,999
Apa?

514
00:36:08,541 --> 00:36:09,626
Tidak benar, 'kan?

515
00:36:10,168 --> 00:36:11,002
Apa?

516
00:36:11,670 --> 00:36:13,088
Kau dan Baeggyul berpacaran.

517
00:36:17,425 --> 00:36:20,136
Kusatukan kalian untuk klub.

518
00:36:20,512 --> 00:36:23,556
Kau terlalu sibuk berkencan
dan UTS-mu gagal.

519
00:36:23,723 --> 00:36:26,226
Pak Cho. Kencan tak ada hubungannya...

520
00:36:26,309 --> 00:36:30,271
Jika itu alasan nilai UTS-mu jelek,
tak masalah.

521
00:36:31,439 --> 00:36:33,858
Jika karena alasan lain,
aku akan membunuhmu.

522
00:36:33,942 --> 00:36:35,694
- Sakit.
- Dasar anak muda.

523
00:36:37,028 --> 00:36:38,613
- Aku iri.
- Sakit sekali.

524
00:36:41,491 --> 00:36:42,951
- Halo.
- Hai, Kitae.

525
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:45,161
- Halo.
- Hai.

526
00:36:57,215 --> 00:36:58,675
<i>Four of a kind.</i>

527
00:36:59,843 --> 00:37:01,511
<i>Jangan pelit.</i>

528
00:37:02,512 --> 00:37:03,346
Hai, Kitae.

529
00:37:03,430 --> 00:37:04,848
Halo, Pak.

530
00:37:04,931 --> 00:37:07,100
Ada apa? Bukankah belnya berbunyi?

531
00:37:07,183 --> 00:37:08,393
Ya.

532
00:37:09,227 --> 00:37:12,647
Tapi... ada sesuatu
yang harus segera kukatakan.

533
00:37:14,816 --> 00:37:17,569
Tadi, saat aku di kamar mandi.

534
00:37:19,028 --> 00:37:20,738
Aku melihat ini di tempat sampah.

535
00:37:33,126 --> 00:37:34,752
Mari kita baca dengan lantang.

536
00:37:36,129 --> 00:37:38,798
"Anggota masyarakat

537
00:37:38,882 --> 00:37:43,178
mengancam keselamatan dan ketertiban
masyarakat dengan tindakan ilegal.

538
00:37:43,762 --> 00:37:45,597
Lalu otoritas pemerintah

539
00:37:45,680 --> 00:37:48,808
menghukum mereka

540
00:37:48,892 --> 00:37:51,352
untuk menjaga ketertiban."

541
00:37:52,103 --> 00:37:53,271
Tentu saja.

542
00:37:55,356 --> 00:37:56,191
Aku setuju.

543
00:37:57,192 --> 00:38:00,945
Namun, jangan hanya membaca kata-kata ini.

544
00:38:01,529 --> 00:38:03,031
Mari berpikir kritis.

545
00:38:04,157 --> 00:38:07,285
Siapa mereka
hingga bisa menghukum seseorang?

546
00:38:08,286 --> 00:38:09,788
Siapa di dunia ini

547
00:38:10,914 --> 00:38:12,040
yang memberi mereka

548
00:38:12,790 --> 00:38:14,292
wewenang untuk melakukan itu?

549
00:38:15,919 --> 00:38:18,379
Halo, Bu Baek. Maaf mengganggu kelasmu.

550
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:19,798
Ada apa?

551
00:38:19,881 --> 00:38:21,674
- Boleh minta waktu sebentar?
- Ya.

552
00:38:21,758 --> 00:38:23,760
Aku ingin memeriksa
tas dan loker anak-anak.

553
00:38:23,843 --> 00:38:26,554
Sebenarnya, aku memberikannya
kepada mereka.

554
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:31,351
- Bagaimana bisa?
- Kau sangat sombong.

555
00:38:32,018 --> 00:38:32,977
Dan...

556
00:38:33,812 --> 00:38:35,146
kalian memberikannya.

557
00:38:35,230 --> 00:38:36,648
<i>Kepala sekolah gila datang.</i>

558
00:38:36,731 --> 00:38:38,066
Kita berikan kepada mereka.

559
00:38:38,149 --> 00:38:43,071
Warga biasa seperti kalian dan aku
memberi mereka wewenang.

560
00:38:43,154 --> 00:38:45,949
Semuanya, taruh tas di meja kalian.

561
00:38:48,493 --> 00:38:50,286
Ayo! Lakukan sekarang.

562
00:38:51,663 --> 00:38:52,747
Lakukan.

563
00:38:55,166 --> 00:38:56,209
Mulailah.

564
00:38:56,876 --> 00:38:59,170
<i>Dia memeriksa barang pribadi,</i>
<i>mulai dari kelasku.</i>

565
00:38:59,254 --> 00:39:02,340
Tak peduli betapa sulitnya hidup,

566
00:39:02,423 --> 00:39:05,552
jangan lewati batas ini.

567
00:39:06,094 --> 00:39:07,136
<i>Hei.</i>

568
00:39:07,804 --> 00:39:09,722
<i>Jangan bilang itu masih ada di tasmu.</i>

569
00:39:14,227 --> 00:39:15,436
<i>Hei, periksa ponselmu.</i>

570
00:39:30,577 --> 00:39:35,540
Hukum adalah kesepakatan
semua orang yang ada di masyarakat.

571
00:39:36,124 --> 00:39:38,001
Astaga, kau sangat berdebu!

572
00:39:44,257 --> 00:39:45,258
Semua sudah diperiksa?

573
00:39:45,341 --> 00:39:47,176
<i>Dia hampir selesai.</i>
<i>Kelasmu berikutnya.</i>

574
00:39:47,260 --> 00:39:48,469
Seperti ini.

575
00:40:10,658 --> 00:40:11,826
Pak Cho.

576
00:40:13,786 --> 00:40:15,288
- Halo, Pak Cho.
- Halo.

577
00:40:15,663 --> 00:40:16,998
Apa yang bisa kubantu?

578
00:40:17,916 --> 00:40:18,875
Maaf mengganggu.

579
00:40:20,918 --> 00:40:22,045
Ini...

580
00:40:23,379 --> 00:40:24,464
Ini tak akan lama.

581
00:40:25,340 --> 00:40:26,424
Baiklah.

582
00:40:27,216 --> 00:40:28,426
Perhatian.

583
00:40:28,968 --> 00:40:29,802
Hari ini,

584
00:40:30,595 --> 00:40:32,138
ini ditemukan

585
00:40:33,556 --> 00:40:34,474
di kamar mandi.

586
00:40:35,683 --> 00:40:37,727
Jadi, sekarang kami akan

587
00:40:38,269 --> 00:40:40,063
menggeledah barang pribadi semua orang.

588
00:40:40,730 --> 00:40:43,399
Keluarkan isi tas kalian di atas meja.

589
00:40:44,484 --> 00:40:45,318
Sekarang!

590
00:41:00,708 --> 00:41:01,751
Pak.

591
00:41:02,251 --> 00:41:05,630
Secara resmi, kau butuh persetujuan siswa.

592
00:41:08,508 --> 00:41:09,634
Siapa yang tak setuju?

593
00:41:11,678 --> 00:41:12,512
Ada?

594
00:41:15,473 --> 00:41:16,307
Tak ada, 'kan?

595
00:41:16,808 --> 00:41:18,643
Sekarang, taruh tas kalian di meja.

596
00:41:20,353 --> 00:41:22,814
Jika loker kalian dikunci,

597
00:41:22,897 --> 00:41:25,483
bukalah sekarang.

598
00:41:26,317 --> 00:41:28,820
Cepat.

599
00:41:28,903 --> 00:41:30,863
Berdiri sekarang!

600
00:41:41,666 --> 00:41:42,542
Aku.

601
00:41:46,087 --> 00:41:47,088
Kau apa?

602
00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:48,339
Aku tak setuju.

603
00:41:51,843 --> 00:41:52,677
Apa?

604
00:41:53,094 --> 00:41:55,221
Aku tak setuju digeledah...

605
00:41:58,391 --> 00:41:59,600
Aku tak bisa setuju.

606
00:42:02,937 --> 00:42:07,316
JIKA KENAL REMAJA YANG KESULITAN,
